---
description: Clinic gateway, offline operation and synchronization invariants
globs: ["services/sync-engine/**", "services/local-*/**", "apps/desktop/**", "packages/sync-contracts/**"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- The clinic gateway is the operational authority during an internet outage.
- Use transactional outbox/inbox, event IDs, idempotency keys, versions and cursors.
- Never use blind table copying or generic last-write-wins for clinical/financial data.
- Different-field edits may merge; same-field conflicts require review.
- One failed sync item must not block unrelated items.
- Enforce read-only mode after 72 hours without successful cloud sync.
- Test interruption, replay, duplicate events and cross-clinic conflicts.
